### ID
DAL-DEV-0014

### Project
Deviation

### Type
Deviation

### Title
Incorrect Filter Provided by Distributor

Upon filling of Norepinephrine Bitartrate 8mg/8ml Lot 10000096 on 15OCT24, it was observed that the filter received for sterile filtration was the incorrect filter (non-sterile vs. sterile). Filling was halted and Quality was notified. At this time, two tubs of 10R vials had been filled, stoppered, and capped
. Upon investigation, it was found that non-sterile filters (Cat. No. JKPS020LFLM-GP) were received from the distributor instead of the sterile filters that were purchased (Cat. No. JKPS020LFLM-ETO).
